@startuml sequence_first_draw
!theme plain
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center

title First Draw Closes Entry Window

actor Visitor
participant "DrawPage" as DP
participant "Express API" as API
participant "drawName()" as DRAW
database "PostgreSQL" as DB

note over DB: Raffle active\n3 participants\n0 drawn

Visitor -> DP: Clicks "Draw"
DP -> API: POST /api/public/draw
API -> DRAW: drawName(raffleId)
DRAW -> DB: BEGIN TX
DRAW -> DB: SELECT random undrawn\nFOR UPDATE SKIP LOCKED
DB --> DRAW: "Alice"
DRAW -> DB: UPDATE isDrawn=true,\ndrawnAt=NOW(), drawOrder=1
DB --> DRAW: OK
DRAW -> DB: COMMIT
DRAW --> API: { name: "Alice", drawOrder: 1 }
API --> DP: 200 { result }

note over DB: drawnCount = 1\n**Entry window now closed**

@enduml
